    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:radial-gradient(at 40% 20%, #007A8615 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 80% 0%, #99564F10 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 0% 50%, #67C5D112 0px, transparent 50%), var(--surface-light);background-color:var(--surface-light);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"pointer-events: none; inset: 0; position: absolute; opacity: 0.04; background: var(--texture-grain); z-index: 1\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:80px 44px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;text-align:center;gap:var(--space-2);\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=100\" alt=\"Sarah Kim\" style=\"width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;border:3px solid white;\"><p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#070C0D;line-height:1.2;margin:0;\">\u201cThe ROI was obvious in week one. We went from dreading content deadlines to shipping carousels before lunch.\u201d</p><div><div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:15px;font-weight:900;color:#070C0D;\">Sarah Kim</div><div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:12px;color:#394546;\">Design Lead, Relay.so</div></div></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
