    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:var(--surface-dark);background-color:var(--surface-dark);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"opacity: 0.04; z-index: 1; pointer-events: none; inset: 0; background: var(--texture-grain); position: absolute\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:72px 44px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:#E7F0F2;margin:0;line-height:1.08;\">Deal Collateral: Before vs After</h2>\n            <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto 1fr;gap:var(--space-1);align-items:stretch;\">\n                <div style=\"border-radius:0;padding:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:1px solid #1B3235;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;color:#EF4444;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:0.06em;\">BEFORE</div>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:var(--text-sm);color:#C3D1D3;line-height:1.45;margin:0;\">Before: Sales requests design team 5 days before demo. Gets generic deck. Customizes 2 slides. Feels unprofessional.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#3295A1;font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:22px;font-weight:900;\">\u2192</div>\n                <div style=\"border-radius:0;padding:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:1px solid #1B3235;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;color:#3295A1;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:0.06em;\">AFTER</div>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:var(--text-sm);color:#C3D1D3;line-height:1.45;margin:0;\">After: Sales runs nexus generate 30 min before demo. Gets prospect-specific carousel with their logo, data, and pain points.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"margin-top:14px;border-radius:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:1px solid #1B3235;padding:var(--space-2) 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-1);\">\n                <div style=\"width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:0;background:#3295A1;color:white;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:16px;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2197</div>\n                <div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:var(--text-sm);font-weight:800;color:#E7F0F2;line-height:1.45;\">5 days \u2192 30 min</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
