    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:radial-gradient(at 40% 20%, #007A8615 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 80% 0%, #99564F10 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 0% 50%, #67C5D112 0px, transparent 50%), var(--surface-light);background-color:var(--surface-light);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"pointer-events: none; position: absolute; z-index: 1; background: var(--texture-grain); inset: 0; opacity: 0.04\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:72px 44px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:#070C0D;margin:0;line-height:1.08;\">From Cost Center to Revenue Driver</h2>\n            <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;\">\n                <div style=\"border-radius:0;padding:18px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #BDCACC;\"><div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:#EF4444;margin-bottom:8px;\">PROBLEM</div><p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:var(--text-sm);color:#394546;line-height:1.45;margin:0;\">Content team was seen as a cost center \u2014 necessary but slow. Leadership questioned whether the investment was justified.</p></div>\n                <div style=\"border-radius:0;padding:18px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #BDCACC;\"><div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:#007A86;margin-bottom:8px;\">SOLUTION</div><p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:var(--text-sm);color:#394546;line-height:1.45;margin:0;\">With Nexus, the content team now runs 3x more campaigns with the same headcount. Attribution shows content-driven pipeline grew 180%.</p></div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #BDCACC;border-radius:0;padding:12px 16px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:#007A86;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:4px;\">KEY IMPACT & PROOF</div>\n                <div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:11px;color:#394546;line-height:1.45;\">180% pipeline growth &nbsp;\u2022&nbsp; 3x campaign velocity &nbsp;\u2022&nbsp; Content ROI positive in 30 days</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
