ans;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:#2E929E;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:4px;\">KEY IMPACT & PROOF</div>\n                <div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:11px;color:#C3D1D3;line-height:1.45;\">Pipeline Growth &nbsp;\u2022&nbsp; Team Budget Increase</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
